source.name: EOM April FY 11  Education Recipients by Training Type and VA Education Benefit Program
source.description: FY 11 Education Recipients by training type  and VA Education Benefit Program (Through Feb. FY11). The data represents the number of individuals by VA education program who have used their VA education benefit during fiscal year 2011(Through the April. FY11). Training type statistics may include individuals who used their education benefits in more than one training type, therefore the total within this table may be different than the total number of beneficiaries during the fiscal year.
